extendedInfo.description: Live wallpaper that displays a selected gallery image. - Select transition between home screens! - Supports wide-screen and panorama wallpapers! - Customize portrait/landscape settings separately (if supported by launcher).For more transitions, including 3D cube effect, check out the full version.
